@startuml
title Vectis MVP Package Diagram

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam linetype ortho

package "src" {
  package "website" as Website
  package "webapp" as Webapp
  package "backend" as Backend
  package "shared" as Shared
}

database "Future Postgres" as Postgres
queue "Future Broker" as Broker
collections "Future Object Store" as ObjectStore

Website ..> Shared : product messaging\nsample content
Webapp ..> Shared : types and seeded data
Backend ..> Shared : contracts and sample resources

Webapp --> Backend : REST /api/v1
Backend ..> Postgres : planned persistence
Backend ..> Broker : planned event dispatch
Backend ..> ObjectStore : planned media storage

note bottom of Shared
Shared currently contains
TypeScript contracts and
seeded MVP fixtures.
end note

@enduml
